  "instructions": [
    "Whisk rice vinegar, soy sauce, sesame oil, minced ginger, minced garlic, and chili flakes in a small bowl.",
    "Toss shredded carrots, sliced cucumber, and sliced red bell pepper in a large bowl until coated with the dressing.",
    "Gently fold in sliced nectarines, keeping them intact.",
    "Sprinkle seaweed flakes over the salad and stir lightly to distribute.",
    "Top with toasted sesame seeds for crunch.",
    "Transfer the salad onto a slate tile for presentation.",
    "Cover and refrigerate for 15 minutes to meld flavors.",
    "Serve chilled as a crisp date-night dish."
  ],
